cross: Phalaenopsis Lioulin Topaz x Phalaenopsis Jiuhbao Golden Diamond
location: National Cheng Kung University Fall Orchid Show, Taiwan

measurements.description: Nine flowers and four buds on one 81-cm arching inflorescence; sepals and petals lemon ice, white proximally; lip open, tri-lobed, light lemon ice, white picotee, callus light lemon ice; anther cap white; substance firm; texture crystalline.
